/**
 * @brief
 *    This App allows the wakeup button to support short press sleep/wakeup,
 * Long press shutdown/boot system .
 *
 * NOTE:
 *   1. please use getevent command to confirm the BUTTON_EVENT of the gpio_key;
 *   2. this gpio_key must be wakeup_key and defined as the corresponding value of the EVENT_CODE; this value can also be obtained using the getevent command.
 *
 * Add this module in the project:
 *   device/\<board\>/\<board\>_base.mk:PRODUCT_MODULES += spm
 *
 * @author Ingenic
 *
 * @version 1.0.0
 */
